  m_Name: TakasuRyuuji
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::CharacterInfo
  characterName: Takasu Ryuuji
  description: A stay-at-home dad who always takes great care of his family. He goes
    to great lengths to ensure that his children are well-fed and his wife comes
    back from work to a clean home. While the people around him fear the glare from
    his sanpaku eyes, his children seek comfort in his gentle gaze. Even though his
    daughters struggle at school and his wife gets stressed from her role as a mother,
    he continues to work to his strengths, ensuring his meals put bright smiles on
    their faces.
